data.description: Rare opportunity to purchase this magnificent 4/2.5 single family home located in prestigious Kingsview at Towngate. This stunning home has been completely renovated from top to bottom and features a brand-new barrel style metal roof, impact windows and doors throughout the entire property, large state of the art kitchen with top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, marble waterfall center island and quartz countertops. Step out from the kitchen onto the large, air-conditioned Florida Room with an outdoor kitchen. perfect for entertaining! The extended master suite features a large sitting area with a bay window and spacious his and her closets. The exquisite luxury spa feeling master bathroom features his and her vanities with a large centerpiece bathtub and separate shower.
